\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n\t\t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t    \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-18\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001111_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001111.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>ἱερ\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" evidence=\"previouseditor\">οθ\u003C/supplied>υτέοντος Φάωνος\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>Νύ\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">μ\u003C/supplied>\u003Csupplied reason=\"undefined\" evidence=\"previouseditor\">φ\u003C/supplied>ωνος Σωπολιανοῦ,\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>ἀγορ\u003Cunclear>α\u003C/unclear>νομέοντος Ξενάρχου\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>Ἀπολλ\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" evidence=\"previouseditor\">οδώ\u003C/supplied>ρου καὶ τὰν ἐπιμέλειαν\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>πο\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" evidence=\"previouseditor\">ι\u003Csupplied reason=\"omitted\">η\u003C/supplied>σαμ\u003C/supplied>ένου τῶν ἔργων vacat\n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\"/>ἁ \u003Cunclear>ᾀ\u003C/unclear>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">γ\u003C/supplied>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" evidence=\"previouseditor\">ο\u003C/supplied>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ρ\u003C/supplied>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" evidence=\"previouseditor\">ὰ\u003C/supplied> κατεσκευάσθη\n                 \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text of Ampolo and Erdas 2019\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    \u003C!--Lists the various local mag's in charge at the time that either cleaning, or construction of a colonnade was undertaken, by Diodoros. Cited in discussion of gymnasia evidence by Nenci, 1991, 923; note that Delorme 1960: 288 n.7, 487 rejected the restoration of the word 'xystos', which goes back to 1836, and with that rejection, the link to a gymnasium becomes tenuous to say the least. But generally cited in support of existence of Segestan gymnasium. Nenci 1991, 924 for date, and cf. SEG 41.825.-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IG\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Kaibel\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1890\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\">290\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRan